{"tid":2208332,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個，講出嚟會令人葡萄嘅返工地點","createTime":"2020-09-18T22:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T20:00:01.000Z","uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d9040049c4d635de2ef4c6baba0100e9757556b7","tid":2208332,"uid":284284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T22:15:34.000Z","msg":"我先：希慎廣場office tower, 朗豪坊office tower"},{"pid":"cf98c2e95c9259a22f75b2196cd8e25dfc534e95","tid":2208332,"uid":299944,"like":145,"dislike":0,"score":145,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T22:17:19.000Z","msg":"Home office"},{"pid":"691899a6e9c225a41ec448038f89968c91e5e625","tid":2208332,"uid":345696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T22:18:14.000Z","msg":"屋企"},{"pid":"1150ceb9ac41f95045a78e8b8017c8d6e8fbb6b5","tid":2208332,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T22:20:15.000Z","msg":"Landmark IFC <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最正就係自己屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445a0cdfa8e867df3f56331f36602067d47d62d7","tid":2208332,"uid":238301,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T22:32:14.000Z","msg":"花園道26號"},{"pid":"b8d94c1aaa1140e68134d8253bb52e3977de0534","tid":2208332,"uid":105890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T22:33:11.000Z","msg":"九龍區得icc 係掂"},{"pid":"3aaa69d779d91bd5a9a4ec894e0150e468d6ab7f","tid":2208332,"uid":35746,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T22:33:15.000Z","msg":"國際太空站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3389b989065e028be926409c672441a503529a53","tid":2208332,"uid":142854,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T22:34:21.000Z","msg":"我做麥當勞。。。前日最後兩個男仔都走埋<br />\n<br />\n我做左7年了。呢7年黎我都溝左唔同男朋友，但最後佢地都離我而去。。。每次有新男仔入職時 我都會不停撩佢傾計 有時會問下佢d有趣問題 例如一張m巾可以吸幾多杯麥旋風 用bra包住豬柳蛋俾客仔會唔會好正 著真空炸薯條會唔會好味d 佢地都好怕羞咁笑 相處氣氛幾好<br />\n<br />\n到有幾次我見佢炸緊薯條機會黎了捉住佢手仔佢冇出聲我就知道得米了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果陣時日日追住佢返工放工 lunch佢自己一個出去好遠既餐廳食我又扮撞到搭佢枱🙈🙈🙈諗起都好sweet<br />\n<br />\n而且佢放工又成日避開我好怕醜🙈🙈🙈 諗起都好sweet sweet啊<br />\n<br />\n有次放工我約佢睇戲 佢話去個廁所先 點知我係出面等左個幾鐘都未出黎 我就主動入去搵佢啦 我爬上廁格上面逐格望 係最後一格上面望到佢 原來佢同緊人WhatsApp唔記得左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我即刻跳落去抱實佢 佢sweet到大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢地全部都係拍拖無耐就辭左工了，又唔聽我電話，男人真係花心...我都想要個穩定既男朋友啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012a46e75b1ddd19bac60e607705f34b0cdb4fdc","tid":2208332,"uid":69014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"445a0cdfa8e867df3f56331f36602067d47d62d7","tid":2208332,"uid":238301,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T22:32:14.000Z","msg":"花園道26號"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:39:25.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n<br />\n之前想申請做佢個internship<br />\n因為做領事館聽落好似獨特啲威水啲（仲要係美領）<br />\n但見到佢係no pay<br />\n又好似要填好多表咁<br />\n最後都係冇申請到"},{"pid":"c3adeb43b887992bb9105b6ed4a3ba037f01576e","tid":2208332,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:40:42.000Z","msg":"人民大會堂"},{"pid":"0e4d551f5d5f2da9fcb2e9451cd0d5134a2318fb","tid":2208332,"uid":63934,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:56:33.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0fbc76cb32